🎯 INTERVIEW POINTS
🔹 Static Members

✅ Belong to Class
✅ Loaded Once
✅ Shared by All Objects
✅ Stored in Method Area

🔹 Instance Members

✅ Belong to Object
✅ New Copy for Every Object
✅ Stored in Heap Memory

